{"tid":1664344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果清算警隊之時，可唔可以連埋8月後仲未辭職既撚樣一齊清算","createTime":"2019-10-20T04:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T14:08:49.000Z","uid":47268,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"57dcd9eb54831ac1eb24f970a8d67fe2ff912b11","tid":1664344,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"好似話近排有好多黑狗驚撚咗美國人權法<br />\n開始多人辭職<br />\n但班撚樣跟本之前一樣喺前線打得好撚開心<br />\n<br />\n有冇可能好似法國以前咁<br />\n所有罪犯既罪名都跟足一世<br />\n8月後仲未辭職既撚樣呢一世都要掛住黑警呢個罪名<br />\n等佢之後去旅行，移民，見工<br />\n都要比人歧視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔想比班柒頭喺制裁前嗰幾日辭職就甩到身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923f381a3fe44299e53eb16738120f867e0e2cea","tid":1664344,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:35:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3b565e39d7e46175b04173e10f6769735f8ee5e","tid":1664344,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:35:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd9738af52141faea146a337de23299d2cf05fa0","tid":1664344,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:35:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fe01b78d8931d7100273f393d5affa8c32813d4","tid":1664344,"uid":49809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89711d38d3a0e062f695aa592c0b9c9db88f7608","tid":1664344,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"其實有冇可能做到"},{"pid":"011581f357e4ad3373c5e5c6c8fd66c55471caad","tid":1664344,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea28a95d87261d038af8379de45416f472afbe88","tid":1664344,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:39:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6df415551aacb98eef5310f24d1b16556b9ca769","tid":1664344,"uid":11160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04: